data.description: Motivated Seller! Full brick ranch style home located in one of Covington's sought after swim/tennis community. Walk to the historical Covington Square or ride in your golf car for shopping, dining and entertainment. This home features 3 large bedrooms, 2.5 bath, with many upgrades. The master is oversized with his and her closets. Large laundry room, open formal dining room, living/great room with built-in shelves. Large kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The pre-framed unfinished basement is awaiting your persona touches.
